<plot>With light-drenched visuals illuminating a screenplay of "dialogue and poetry," filmmaker Gerson made this short B&amp;W experimental feature about a man who confronts the meaning of existence in a variety of cityscapes. Gerson described the film: "The narrative form expanded, utilizing non-linear sequences within a linear structure. Past, Present and Future are interwoven throughout to present a total, heightened reality."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?578713</url></doc>
